name: harvesting, use of harvesting cart | harvesting, use of harvesting cart | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/29808/documentation

This dataset represents the service of harvesting 1 kg of maize by a harvesting cart. It has an operational time of 0.001605 h/ha and a lifetime operational time is 1200 h. Its fuel consumption is 0.015245 kg diesel per kg of harvesting maize, while it weighs 1500 kg. The yield of maize in the US is 107945 hg/ha.

The process starts when the harvesting cart is on the agricultural field to be harvested

This activity ends with the delivery of harvested maize. The dataset includes the diesel fuel consumption and the amount of agricultural machinery and of the shed attributed to harvesting. It was also taken into consideration the amount of emissions to the air from combustion and the emission to the soil from tyre abrasion during the work process.
